<html lang='en'>
	<head>
		<meta charset='UTF-8' />
		<meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0' />
		<title>Welcome to the Team!</title>
		<style type='text/css'>
			body { font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif; margin: 0; padding: 20px; background-color: #f4f4f4; color: #333; }
			.container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background: #fff; padding: 20px; border-radius: 5px; box-shadow: 0
			0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); } h2, h3 { color: #5d6975; } h2 { font-size: 22px; text-align: center; padding: 20px 0;
			} h3 { font-size: 18px; padding: 10px 0; } p, li { font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; } .checklist {
			list-style-type: none; padding: 0; } .checklist li:before { content: 'âœ“'; margin-right: 8px; color: #6da34d; } /*
			Mobile responsiveness */ @media (max-width: 600px) { .container { width: 100%; padding: 10px; box-shadow: none; }
			h2 { font-size: 20px; } h3 { font-size: 16px; } p, li { font-size: 14px; } }
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<div class='container'>
			<h2 style='font-size: 22px; text-align: center; padding: 20px 0; color: #5d6975;'>Welcome Aboard, {{name}}!</h2>
			<p style='font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;'>We're thrilled to have you on board. If you have any questions, feel
				free to contact us at
				{{support_email}}.</p>
			<h3 style='font-size: 18px; padding: 10px 0; color: #5d6975;'>Onboarding Checklist</h3>
			<ul class='checklist' style='list-style-type: none; padding: 0;'>
				<li style='font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;'>Set up your company email account</li>
				<li style='font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;'>Complete your profile on our internal platform</li>
				<li style='font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;'>Schedule your first team meeting</li>
				<li style='font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;'>Read through the employee handbook</li>
			</ul>
			<h3 style='font-size: 18px; padding: 10px 0; color: #5d6975;'>Interesting Facts</h3>
			<p style='font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;'>Did you know? Our company was founded in the year
				{{foundation_year}}
				and has been on an incredible journey ever since!</p>
			<p style='font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;'>Another fact: We have employees from over
				{{number_of_countries}}
				different countries!</p>
		</div>
	</body>
</html>